        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 2: Duties of constituent institutions</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 3: Duties of students’ unions</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Part 2: Functions of the Office for Students</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 5: General functions</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 6: Regulation of duties of registered higher education providers</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 7: Regulation of duties of students’ unions</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 8: Complaints scheme</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 9: Overseas funding</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 10: Director for Freedom of Speech and Academic Freedom</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Part 3: General</inline></tocItem>
